::Feline::

She nodded to Zardus, "Yes,right away," she said with a soft purr at 
Zardus.  She saw the other bot next to him.  The scent of the bot 
made her noce twitch and tickle.  Something wasn't right. But anyway, 
she had her orders.  She went to the computer and entered in the 
programming sequence 2393a as Zardus instucted.  She then watched and 
the femme bot on the table twitched and moved slghtly as the program 
started to run.
